{
  "stem": "5644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a lot of talk that we start off later, but we got documentation that we start in '39.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went right through, not very strong in '39, but slowly over the years we build it up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the first one to start the-- the underground, because the ZOB started much later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ZOB started in 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean '39?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zero.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't one of them at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was Appelbaum and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appelbaum and another three people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other three were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his contact with the Polish underground or the AK--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That wasn't AK in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The organization was called differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think, if I'm not mistaking--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To help them, to train them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have a ghetto at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To train them and to give them guns and ammunitions and to help them with guns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was done in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a gift.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know that will sound very, very little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we did have four guns in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not we, but the four leaders did get four guns from him as a gift immediately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was done in a manner that's-- as far as Iwanska's concerned, Iwanska did help on his own accord, not even in some cases advising his own organization.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not advising, even.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because Iwanska did give a lot to the Jewish people during the resistance all together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's rare to mention his name, because Iwanska lost his son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He lost his brother in the fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was very heavily wounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a story-- I don't know how far it is true or not true.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I can't say it, because I never checked it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
